Trade/Device Name(s): Dimension® EXLTM with LM clinical chemistry system
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Dimension® EXLTM with LM clinical chemistry system
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Dimension EXLTM with LM clinical chemistry system, FT4L Flex reagent cartridge and LOCI Thyroid Calibrator for quantitative measurement of Free Thyroxine and calibration in serum/plasma.
Indications for Use Summary: Quantitative measurement of Free Thyroxine in human serum and plasma for diagnosis and monitoring of thyroid disease; calibration of FT4L method on Dimension EXLTM with LM system.
